Class DateTimeConstantsAdapter

java.lang.Object
com.google.gwt.i18n.client.DateTimeConstantsAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
DateTimeConstants
class DateTimeConstantsAdapter extends Object implements DateTimeConstants
Adapter that makes a DateTimeFormatInfo implementation suitable for use with something that wants a DateTimeConstants.
